<div id="review_2386403098" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2386403098" />
    <a title="Sophia Triad" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/44642860-sophia-triad"><img alt="Sophia Triad" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1620230289p2/44642860.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2386403098?book_show_action=true">May 09, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sophia Triad" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sophia Triad" href="/user/show/44642860-sophia-triad">Sophia Triad</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44642860-sophia-triad?shelf=children">children</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2386403098" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10720000834901933508">Another awesome adventure with the whiny and clueless but still lovable pigeon.<br/><br/>Pigeon wants a puppy, but he hasn&apos;t realised what kind of care and how much care the puppy will need.<br/><i> Oh don&apos;t worry. I&apos;ll take care of it.<br/>I promise I&apos;ll water it once per month.</i><br/><br/>A very good book if you want to discuss with your children the difficulties of having a pet and how much responsible they must be in order to keep their pet happy AND ALIVE.<br/><br/>We have just got this from the library and most probably we will read </span>
  <span id="freeText10720000834901933508" style="display:none">Another awesome adventure with the whiny and clueless but still lovable pigeon.<br /><br />Pigeon wants a puppy, but he hasn't realised what kind of care and how much care the puppy will need.<br /><i> Oh don't worry. I'll take care of it.<br />I promise I'll water it once per month.</i><br /><br />A very good book if you want to discuss with your children the difficulties of having a pet and how much responsible they must be in order to keep their pet happy AND ALIVE.<br /><br />We have just got this from the library and most probably we will read it every night this week. Unfortunately we will run out of "pigeon books" very soon :(<br /></span>
