      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lisa  (not getting friends updates) Vegan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lisa  (not getting friends updates) Vegan" href="/user/show/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan">Lisa  (not getting friends updates) Vegan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=childrens">childrens</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=zz-3star">zz-3star</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=readbooks-male-author-or-illust">readbooks-male-author-or-illust</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=picture-books">picture-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=dogs">dogs</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=reviewed">reviewed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/83445-lisa-not-getting-friends-updates-vegan?shelf=z2008">z2008</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer37492721" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4150418090893356189">This is a very, very, very simple book; the text and illustrations are both very spare. It’s also funny and great for beginning readers and younger children. As a puppy loving person I enjoyed it even though it’s much more about the pigeon than the puppy. The story was almost too simple for me but it had an amusing enough “surprise” ending.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


