<span id="freeTextContainer10892608044345886746">Continuing with his lovable Pigeon, Mo Willems creates a narrative in which the pigeon really, really wants a puppy.  After all, they&apos;re just so adorable!  With a minimalist and cartoonish style, Willems knows just how to exaggerate and when to pull back--his images and text are easily inferred by small minds, and they&apos;re sure to entertain!  Great for the kid who wants a pet, or who just really likes animals.  Perfect for grades K-2.<br/><br/>Review cross-listed <a href='http://www.littleladylibrarian.wordpress.com' rel='nofollow noopener'>here</a>!</span>
